Hosting	CodeSandbox / Vercel
State Handling	React Hooks (useState, useEffect)
ğŸŒ API References
1ï¸âƒ£ Geocoding API

Converts a city name to latitude and longitude.

Example:

https://geocoding-api.open-meteo.com/v1/search?name=Chennai


Response:

{
  "results": [
    {
      "latitude": 13.08784,
      "longitude": 80.27847,
      "name": "Chennai",
      "country": "India"
    }
  ]
}

2ï¸âƒ£ Weather API

Fetches current and forecast weather data.

Example:

https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=13.08784&longitude=80.27847&current_weather=true


Response:

{
  "current_weather": {
    "temperature": 31.5,
    "windspeed": 12.3,
    "weathercode": 1
  }
}

